arts.ttl: Port Vale return to winning ways with comfortable victory against MK Dons
arts.sum: Lorent Tolaj and Jayden Stockley scored in the first half to cement their place in the League Two play-offs after a four-match winless streak.

arts.ttl: Port Vale-Milton Keynes Dons Statistical Preview
